{"tid":351554,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 烤法式春雞釀炒飯","createTime":"2017-08-08T07:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T01:53:46.000Z","uid":30742,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e63aeee4507e682ac30e213190d7e4484832dfbe","tid":351554,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/aU4Lz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FaU4Lz.jpg&h=6a25d766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FTdcvG0EUko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFTdcvG0EUko&d=gdiYxCtBTdaFGM%2Brub%2BvXP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=428589a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FTdcvG0EUko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個星期六朝早，如無特別我都會去巡超市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇特價野！諗下呢兩日食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （窮人等特價）<br />\n前幾個星期見到無啦啦有特價春雞，仲要法式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁好明顯一定唔係法國黎，應該純粹係細細隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都買隻試下啦！ <br />\n返到去望真d又覺得兩個人會唔夠食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩屋企有冷飯，就求其炒左個飯塞入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又順便將雪櫃d菜墊底焗埋去<br />\n出到黎都見得下人<br />\n仲要一煲有齊肉、菜和澱粉質<br />\n方便齊料又夠晒飽<br />\n可以有下次！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜：<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/08/stuffed-spring-chicken-with-fried-rice.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F08%2Fstuffed-spring-chicken-with-fried-rice.html&d=gdiYxCtBTdaFGM%2Brub%2BvXP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=61827381\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/08/stuffed-spring-chicken-with-fried-rice.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=gdiYxCtBTdaFGM%2Brub%2BvXP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1833c7fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=gdiYxCtBTdaFGM%2Brub%2BvXP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9bf43d8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=gdiYxCtBTdaFGM%2Brub%2BvXP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6d4b88bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"b6c7cb44190e89b699274e4f401ff6880e16ef51","tid":351554,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380a24d81f99411d824175c13ebdad3c12d22b7e","tid":351554,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 